To install
==========

cd <parent_dir_to_this_dir>
s3.install_all.sh

All scripts are now accessible via sc.*.sh commands

How to use
==========

The following operates on indifidual files:
-------------------------------------------
sc.signal-edit.sh       Edits a specific signal (*.sig)
sc.sample-edit.sh       Edits a specific sample (*.smpl)

The following operates on directories:
--------------------------------------
sc.sigdef_pack.sh       Take a directory with *sig files and one *.smpl
                        file and convert it into a sampler *.ini file.
sc.sigdef_unpack.sh     Reverse the operation above. I.e. from a *.ini
						file create directory with *.sig files (and possibly
						one *.smpl file)


